String Class:
 	String is the most widely used class in Java. It helps us store and manipulate test based data.


why we should learn about string class and its method:
	String class has a lot of methods that can help us manipulate the text based data.
	that why we don't need to write any logic we can simple create the object of the string class and  can use the method form that class.
	
